Maintainer: Who to complain to <yourfault@somewhere.net>
Description: Provides functions to simulate and estimate Response Time Multilevel
    Latent Class (RTMLC) IRT models for the joint analysis of response accuracy
    and response time in multilevel item-response data. The model relies on
    discrete latent variables at both the individual and cluster levels and
    allows individual- and cluster-level covariates to be included in both the
    response accuracy and response time components.
